work.work-title: Come, let us with our Lord arise

credit.credit-words: This is the day the Lord has made, that all may see his love displayed, may feel his resurrection's power, and rise again to fall no more, in perfect righteousness renewed, and filled with all the life of God.
Come, let us with our Lord arise
